        "action": "Fund more training for teachers on neurodivergence",
        "additional_details": "Neurodivergence, which includes conditions such as autism, ADHD, dyslexia, and other cognitive differences, represents a diverse spectrum of learning needs that we feel are often overlooked or misunderstood in school.",
        "background": "We want the government to fund more comprehensive training programs for teachers on how to effectively support and engage neurodivergent students in the classroom.",
